## ‚ûï Append Example

```python
from filehandler import FileHandler, FileHandleMode

fh = FileHandler(FileHandleMode.Modern)

fh.append('~/Documents/logfile.txt', {'event': 'login', 'user': 'charlie'})
fh.append('~/Documents/logfile.txt', "raw string log entry")

